<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>自定义弹窗</title>
    <style>
        .custom-alert {
            position: fixed;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            z-index: 1000;
        }
        .custom-alert button {
            padding: 5px 10px;
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>页面内容</h1>
    <p>页面加载时会显示自定义弹窗。</p>

    <div id="customAlert" class="custom-alert" style="display: none;">
        <h3>自定义弹窗</h3>
        <p>这是一个 HTML + CSS 模拟的弹窗。</p>
        <button onclick="document.getElementById('customAlert').style.display = 'none'">关闭</button>
    </div>

    <script>
        window.onload = function() {
            document.getElementById("customAlert").style.display = "block";
        };
    </script>
</body>
</html>